data.description: Price Reduction! Beautifully remodeled Courtyard home on the golf course in 55 plus gated Kings Ridge. Home has a large heated inground swim spa with decorative rock and the courtyard is done in paver bricks. Matching paver drive and walkways leading to the courtyard entry. Electric awning in the courtyard for when you want more shade. Separate In Law suite as you enter with it own bathroom. New roof in July 2014. All the windows in the home and the 4 sliders were replaced by Window World. The kitchen has been totally remodeled with new high end cabinetry, granite counter tops, back splash & new stainless steel appliances. Laminate flooring throughout most of the home. Home has a central vacuum system. Half Bath in the main area of home. The Master bedroom has wood look tile and a large walk in closet. The master bathroom has been totally remodeled also. The tub was removed to make room for a large easily accessible walk in shower. New dual vanity, toilet, flooring and extra cabinetry added. Home has a transferrable Stark termite bond. Enjoy the Kings Ridge Royal life style in the multi-million $ clubhouse with 3 heated pools, spas, tennis & pickle ball courts, billiards, shuffle board, shows, Bingo, cards and clubs galore.  The monthly maintenance fees include: lawn maintenance including trimming of shrubs, care of irrigation system & irrigation water, dish cable TV w/ fiber optic cable thru Opticaltel, internet & home phone, maintenance of roads and outside painting of home every 6 years.  Take your golf cart to the Kings Ridge Plaza where you can do your grocery shopping, banking or dine out..
